• an extra TD on return is worth 3.17 points;
• an extra PY/A is worth 61.67 points;
• an extra RY/A is worth 26.44 points;
• an extra TO costs 2.77 points;
• an extra DPY/A costs 67.5 points;
• an extra DRY/A costs 22.79 points;
• an extra forced TO produces 3.49 points; and
• an extra yard in penalties costs 0.06 points.
